unity collaborators</h1>\n556\t            <p>arXivLabs is a framework that allows collaborators to develop and share new arXiv features directly on our website.</p>\n557\t            <p>Both individuals and organizations that work with arXivLabs have embraced and accepted our values of openness, community, excellence, and user data privacy. arXiv is committed to these values and only works with partners that adhere to them.</p>\n558\t            <p>Have an idea for a project that will add value for arXiv's community? <a href=\"https://info.arxiv.org/labs/index.html\"><strong>Learn more about arXivLabs</strong></a>.</p>\n559\t          </div>\n560\t          <div class=\"column is-narrow is-full-mobile\">\n561\t            <p class=\"icon-labs\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" role=\"presentation\" viewBox=\"0 0 635.572 811\"><path d=\"M175.6 676v27h-27v-27zm-54 27v27h27v-27zm-27 27v27h27v-27zm396-54v27h-27v-27zm0 27v27h27v-27zm27 27v27h27v-27zm-27-414h27v27h-27zm27 0h27v-27h-27zm27-27h27v-27h-27zm-396 45h-27v-27h27zm-27-54h-27v27h27zm-27-27h-27v27h27z\"/><path d=\"M94.6 730v27h-27v-27zm477 0v27h-27v-27zm-27-495h27v27h-27zm-450 18h-27v-27h27zm477 9h27v27h-27zm-54 495h27v27h-27zm-423 0h27v27h-27zm-54-504h27v27h-27z\" fill=\"#666\"/><path d=\"M67.6 730v27h-27v-27zm54 54v27h-27v-27zm0-108v27h27v-27zm-27 27v27h27v-27zm-81 0v27h27v-27zm585 27v27h-27v-27zm-108-54v27h27v-27zm27 27v27h27v-27zm81 0v27h27v-27zm-54-495h27v27h-27zm-54 108h27v-27h-27zm27-27h27v-27h-27zm0-81h27v-27h-27zm-423 18h-27v-27h27zm54 54h-27v27h27zm-27-27h-27v27h27zm0-81h-27v27h27zm423 612v27h-27v-27zm81-522v27h-27v-27zm-585-9v27h-27v-27z\" fill=\"#999\"/><path d=\"M94.6 784v27h-27v-27zm-27-27v27h27v-27zm-27-54v27h27v-27zm27 0v27h27v-27zm0-27v27h27v-27zm27 0v27h27v-27zm0-27v27h27v-27zm27 0v27h27v-27zm-108 81v27h27v-27zm558 54v27h-27v-27zm-27-27v27h27v-27zm27-54v27h27v-27zm-27 0v27h27v-27zm0-27v27h27v-27zm-27 0v27h27v-27zm0-27v27h27v-27zm-27 0v27h27v-27zm108 81v27h27v-27zm0-495h27v27h-27zm-27 27h